    <item>
      <title>伊朗支持的激进组织如何扩大以色列-哈马斯战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/iran-s-role-in-israel-hamas-war-will-it-spiral-into-wider-middle-east-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着以色列和巴勒斯坦伊斯兰组织哈马斯之间的战争持续，它引发了中东其他地区的暴力事件。由伊朗支持的激进组织也加入了进来。伊朗支持哈马斯，多年来一直与以色列进行影子战争。他们袭击了以色列目标、红海船只和美军，引发了报复。这些冲突引发了人们的担忧，担心更大范围的大火将席卷该地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/iran-s-role-in-israel-hamas-war-will-it-spiral-into-wider-middle-east-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 19:10:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉马斯瓦米在初选前出售价值 3300 万美元的 Roivant 股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/ramaswamy-sells-33-million-roivant-shares-as-primaries-approach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维韦克·拉马斯瓦米 (Vivek Ramaswamy) 出售了其生物技术公司 Roivant Sciences Ltd. 价值约 3300 万美元的股票，继续用自己的资金主要资助他的总统竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/ramaswamy-sells-33-million-roivant-shares-as-primaries-approach</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 19:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称俄罗斯在乌克兰袭击中使用朝鲜导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/russia-used-north-korean-missiles-in-ukraine-attack-us-alleges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最近几周，作为空中打击的一部分，俄罗斯向乌克兰境内的目标发射了朝鲜提供的导弹，根据最近解密的美国情报评估显示，莫斯科越来越依赖其他国家来发动战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/russia-used-north-korean-missiles-in-ukraine-attack-us-alleges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:47:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着初选临近，特朗普下周将两次出庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/donald-trump-to-appear-in-court-next-week-with-primaries-near</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普计划下周出席在华盛顿和纽约举行的两场大型法庭听证会，这表明随着共和党提名程序的启动，他的法律日程安排得很快就紧张起来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/donald-trump-to-appear-in-court-next-week-with-primaries-near</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:15:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着更广泛战争的风险增加，布林肯再次前往中东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/blinken-is-off-to-mideast-again-as-risk-of-wider-war-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管从红海到黎巴嫩的紧张局势不断升级，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯本周将第四次访问中东，这是自 10 月 7 日以色列遇袭以来，美国继续努力避免更广泛的地区冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/blinken-is-off-to-mideast-again-as-risk-of-wider-war-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 17:42:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登太阳能关税豁免受到美国电池板制造商的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/biden-solar-tariff-holiday-challenged-adding-new-industry-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两家美国太阳能制造商对拜登政府在 6 月初暂停对部分从东南亚进口的电池板征收关税的决定提出质疑，这给已经面临供应链障碍的行业带来了新的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/biden-solar-tariff-holiday-challenged-adding-new-industry-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 17:35:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊斯兰国声称对伊朗致命爆炸事件负责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/islamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-deadly-iran-blasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊斯兰国声称对周三在伊朗发生的袭击事件负责，该袭击造成数十人死亡，并有可能进一步加剧中东紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/islamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-deadly-iran-blasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 17:13:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
